      <h1>Apply to the PharmD Program</h1>
      <p style="line-height: 21.6px;"><strong><a href="#Application Summary" id="Back to Top" name="Back to Top">Application Summary</a></strong><br />
<a href="#step-by-step"><strong>Step-by-Step Application Instructions</strong></a><br />
